o that of Iliopoulos and Zadik (2021), who predicted the absence\nof a computational-statistical gap in the Bernoulli design.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Jun 2022 16:38:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-16"}
