ware testing. However, the lack of discussions about the theme in software\ndevelopment courses, as well as the limited offer of courses focused on\nsoftware quality at the university level reduce the visibility of this area,\nwhich causes a decrease in the interest in this career.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 01:58:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-06-17"}
