\nmetallicity correlation function is not purely the product of a competition\nbetween injection and diffusion. We show that this size scale is generally\nsmaller than 60 pc.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Jun 2022 10:38:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-23"}
